{"tid":2039213,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"元朗再現「走地雞翼尖」","createTime":"2020-05-28T02:05:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-28T05:48:47.000Z","uid":3189,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"2c6d659e94b7053bdd64d4d099e67549f299b781","tid":2039213,"uid":3189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T02:05:39.000Z","msg":"【#飲食熱話】｜元朗再現「走地雞翼尖」<br />\n＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝<br />\n最近有網民分享，指早排經過元朗B仔涼粉店時，見到有工人就咁喺地下洗雞翼尖，上演一場「趴地雞翼尖」，衛生環境非常惡劣! <br />\n<br />\n圖片引起一眾網民討論，有網民指同樣事件已經唔係第一次發生，住喺附近成日會見到，表示唔會再食呢間嘢。本報記者亦有致電查詢，但對方回應「冇啲咁嘅事」。雖然唔知事情真偽，但呢排咁多食物中毒事件，大家真係要食得小心啲呀！<br />\n<br />\n#新假期生活 #新假期飲食熱話 #元朗 #B仔涼粉 #趴地雞翼尖 #雞翼尖 #我話冇就冇 #小心為上 #食前方丈<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FEKjwpP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFEKjwpP.jpg&h=0efd5997&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2cd6a4e3479ab4f8a7cb217c11ecd5a40ab95fd0","tid":2039213,"uid":23833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T02:06:20.000Z","msg":"咪又係食"},{"pid":"6fb80599b3364e7112334b8ce62ab03e3ddc0e91","tid":2039213,"uid":194298,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T02:07:07.000Z","msg":"睇到算好<br />\n睇唔到係屎坑兜住洗都有..."},{"pid":"516c033d576d57f7cd491e03ab2a48138647fa53","tid":2039213,"uid":54927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T02:08:09.000Z","msg":"俾錢食下欄嘢"},{"pid":"e2abe730bd3a9cfbed5399a1c04ad4dfa6c77173","tid":2039213,"uid":115910,"like":2,"dislike":25,"score":-23,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T02:09:26.000Z","msg":"當睇唔到咪算<br />\n分分鐘黃店都係咁洗,做食肆一向拿渣架啦"},{"pid":"b1aab5b244276aec93e99362753c1b72562035bf","tid":2039213,"uid":308595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T02:11:10.000Z","msg":"藍店B仔涼粉?<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f00edd5a5589abea6f54ac20a0c3ed04aaceddf1","tid":2039213,"uid":354205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e2abe730bd3a9cfbed5399a1c04ad4dfa6c7717